#: ../../hardware/controllers/numark_ns6ii.md:18
msgid ""
"The Numark NS6II is an all-in-one USB {term}`MIDI` controller with an "
"integrated audio interface. It has controls for 2 decks that can be toggled "
"between decks to play with 4 decks. Its jogwheels feature a built-in screen "
"highlighting basic information on the currently playing track of each deck."
msgstr ""

